{"an7.36:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.36 ","an7.36:0.2":"4. Devatavagga ","an7.36:0.3":"Pathamamittasutta ","an7.36:1.1":"“Sattahi, bhikkhave, angehi samannagato mitto sevitabbo. ","an7.36:1.2":"Katamehi sattahi? ","an7.36:1.3":"Duddadam dadati, dukkaram karoti, dukkhamam khamati, guyhamassa avi karoti, guyhamassa pariguhati, apadasu na jahati, khinena natimannati. ","an7.36:1.4":"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi angehi samannagato mitto sevitabboti. ","an7.36:2.1":"Duddadam dadati mitto, ","an7.36:2.2":"dukkarancapi kubbati; ","an7.36:2.3":"Athopissa duruttani, ","an7.36:2.4":"khamati dukkhamani ca. ","an7.36:3.1":"Guyhanca tassa akkhati, ","an7.36:3.2":"guyhassa pariguhati; ","an7.36:3.3":"Apadasu na jahati, ","an7.36:3.4":"khinena natimannati. ","an7.36:4.1":"Yamhi etani thanani, ","an7.36:4.2":"samvijjantidha puggale; ","an7.36:4.3":"So mitto mittakamena, ","an7.36:4.4":"bhajitabbo tathavidho”ti. ","an7.36:4.5":"Pancamam. "}